{"title":"小红帽脱险记  ３","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳站得疲倦了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它要回家睡觉了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天顶的黑幕慢慢的扯了下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切怕见阳光的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在准备活动起来做好汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜欢蹦蹦跳跳的小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候好象一段呆木头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧的抱着小脑袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹲在屋角里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一个大大的学问家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在苦苦的想着大大的大问题。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比想一个什么算术式子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要想得更难受，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想呀想的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可想不出什么好办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这比二加二等于四，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更复杂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更复杂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到后来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只急得他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘤嘤嘤的哭起来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“汪汪汪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪汪汪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里来的这个小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲在这里哭啼啼的，羞不羞？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是你呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么哭？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么叫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不是肚子饿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那我可以请你吃两根小骨头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不是干活儿不愿意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那我也可以帮你几把忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我多么羞呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么难为情呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭啼啼的小孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能算一个工作模范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也做不成国家的小主人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“狗大哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不要乱说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是你是我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恐怕早已急得夹起了尾巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲进了你那个烂草窠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不是偷懒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不是肚子饿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伤心的哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁也不来帮助我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要让我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个小人儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就给老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作点心吃掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作点心吃掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想一想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不伤心？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊……妈呀！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个老混蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他今晚要来把你吃掉吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有好法子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定帮你的忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你快快好好的躲起来呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要你相信我，听我的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果老山妖来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看我一定咬得他走不回家。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“狗大哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我谢谢你的好意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一向是老山妖喂养的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替他看门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替他咬人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么现在倒反转来帮助我？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在不多！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在不多！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的好心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在难相信！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在难相信！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（未完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}